Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要去森林里的话  边走边做记号比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很容易迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.38,0:00:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
